<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٨ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٦٦:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ مُسْفِرَةٌ <span class="c2">(٣٨)</span> ضَاحِكَةٌ مُسْتَبْشِرَةٌ <span class="c2">(٣٩)</span> وَوُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ عَلَيْهَا غَبَرَةٌ <span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> تَرْهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ <span class="c2">(٤١)</span> أُولَئِكَ هُمُ الْكَفَرَةُ الْفَجَرَةُ <span class="c2">(٤٢)</span>} <span class="c4">[عبس: ٣٨ - ٤٢]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> <span class="c3">{مُسْفِرَةٌ}</span>: <span class="c2">«مُشْرِقَةٌ»</span>،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> <span class="c3">{تَرْهَقُهَا}</span>: <span class="c2">«تَغْشَاهَا شِدَّةٌ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>